	* Adding ATLAS Ks/Lambda analysis.

2012-02-20  Andy Buckley  <andy.buckley@cern.ch>

	* src/Analyses/ATLAS_2011_I925932.cc: Using new overflow-aware
	normalize() in place of counters and scale(..., 1/count)

